OL,4,C1,350 anniversary year
OL,6,FA Festival of Flame is kickstarting
OL,7,Fthe 1,350th anniversary year of one of
OL,8,FEngland's earliest seats of
OL,9,FChristianity.
OL,11,FHexham Abbey, , marks the milestone
OL,12,Fthis year.
OL,14,FThe abbey will host a number of events
OL,15,Fover the next 12 months, starting with
OL,16,Fthe Festival of Flame over the weekend
OL,17,Fof 2-4 February.
OL,19,FThe light display will include candles
OL,20,Fand music and will be both inside and
OL,21,Foutside the abbey.
