OL,4,C1,350 anniversary year
OL,6,FPeople can also find out more about
OL,7,Fits history through a series of 10
OL,8,Fminute talks on Saturday 3 February.
OL,10,FRevd Canon David Glover, the rector of
OL,11,Fthe abbey, said: "Not many
OL,12,Finstitutions in the world get the
OL,13,Fchance to celebrate 1,350 years of
OL,14,Flife and so this is a really exciting
OL,15,Fyear for the Abbey.
