OL,6,F"Over the next twelve months we will
OL,7,Fgive thanks for all who have
OL,8,Fcontributed to the Abbey's long
OL,9,Fhistory. But we also want to look
OL,10,Fahead and remember that God is calling
OL,11,Fus, in this generation, to keep alive
OL,12,Fthe light of the Gospel. I do hope you
OL,13,Fwill visit the Abbey during the year
OL,14,Fand find a wonderful welcome."
OL,16,FHe will be leading a service,
OL,17,Falongside the Bishop of Newcastle, Rt
OL,18,FRevd Dr Helen-Ann Hartley, to mark the
OL,19,Fstart of the celebrations on Sunday 4
OL,20,FFebruary.
