OL,4,C1,350 anniversary year
OL,6,FThis month will also see 5,000 origami
OL,7,Fstars suspended above the abbey's old
OL,8,Fchoir stalls.
OL,10,FEach star represents a person
OL,11,Fnominated by members of the community.
OL,13,FHexham Abbey dates from 673-74, when
OL,14,FQueen Etheldreda granted Bishop
OL,15,FWilfred the lands of Hexhamshire for a
OL,16,Fnew Benedictine Church, which was
OL,17,Fcompleted in 678.
