OL,6,FOver the next centuries it faced
OL,7,Fattacks from Vikings and Scottish
OL,8,Fraiders, including William Wallace and
OL,9,FRobert Bruce.
OL,11,FWhen the monasteries were dissolved in
OL,12,F1536, Hexham's chancel and transepts
OL,13,Fsurvived because they were needed by
OL,14,Fthe parish church.
OL,16,FIt has undergone various restorations
OL,17,Fover the last two centuries, the most
OL,18,Frecent of which was completed in 2014.
